rComments: Such a kind professor who is really understanding and super passionate about what she teachers. She listens to the students and reflects that in her teaching. The course is writing heavy so if you do the readings and dedicate a good portion of time to the assignments, you'll do great.

My favorite professor. She is a very open minded, liberal, inspiring, curious and lovely person. Her class is very well organized. The assignments can really provide you a systematic training about critical looking. She looks very tender and feminine, but later you will find she is a real feminist inside. She is COOL .Dont miss the chance!
